::Hot Rod::

He noticed what had happaned with IR. 
He wispered to her, "When the fighting starts, be careful. The Matrix
can giv you more power then you might think. When I first had the
Autobot Matrix and became Rodimus Prime, I didn't know my own power, and
I ended up tossing Galvatron across the galaxy."
He then noticed Vehement looking him over. If this bot wanted a fight he
would get the biggest one of his life.
